BUG FIFO-001
Title: rd_valid intermittently not asserted on HIGH priority reads
Severity: Critical
Found By: high_burst_test, starvation_test, full_fifo_test, mixed_test
Design File: design.sv line 285 (high_rd assertion)
Description:
When rd_en=1 and the HIGH priority queue is non-empty, rd_valid is not asserted on every valid output cycle. The DUT's own internal assertion high_rd at design.sv:285 fires repeatedly confirming the bug location.
